&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Five to ten years of experience, with at least a few in trade operations, middle office, or settlement ops at a crypto trading firm, OTC desk, market maker, prime broker, exchange, or TradFi institution. You know post trade: settlement, reconciliation, collateral, counterparty risk, treasury.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hands on experience with the settlement stack trading firms actually use. On the crypto side, that is Fireblocks, ClearLoop, BitGo Go Network, CUBIX, or similar. On the TradFi side, tri party, prime brokerage platforms, or CCP workflows. Post trade and OEMS tools like Talos are a plus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You understand crypto market structure across centralized venues, OTC, and on chain settlement.&lt;/li&gt;
