&lt;p&gt;Crypto trading firms have billions in working capital trapped in bilateral exposures across venues. Cycles Prime frees it. No collateral, no escrow, no new counterparties.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re in pilot with several of the largest trading firms in the market. We’re looking for the founding commercial hire to take us from closed beta to a public release with a real pipeline behind it.&lt;/p&gt;
