&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As Institutional Business Development Lead, you own the pipeline and sales function for Cycles Prime. You build the target list, work the outbound, take the meetings, and push deals to close. As we grow, you hire and build out the BD team, with a path to running Cycles Prime as General Manager.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You arrive with an existing network of buyers at institutional trading firms. You have sold to them before, either at a crypto firm or in TradFi, and you want to apply that to building something new.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;In this role, you will&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Own the pipeline&lt;/strong&gt;. Pick the targets, get the intros, run the meetings. Work the internal stakedholders on their side, negotiate terms, and land new clients.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Own the P&amp;amp;L.&lt;/strong&gt; Help set pricing, fee structure, and the partnership terms we offer early network members. Own the revenue forecast as we grow.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Build the BD function.&lt;/strong&gt; Turn what&#39;s working into the playbook for the next hires. Hire and lead the BD team as we scale, then take over as GM with full P&amp;amp;L.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
