&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Five to ten years selling into institutional markets. Business development or sales at a crypto trading firm or TradFi institution.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have closed real enterprise deals and carried revenue against a quota or pipeline target.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You bring an existing network of buyers at institutional trading firms.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You understand crypto market structure across centralized venues, OTC, and on chain settlement.&lt;/li&gt;
